# OpenFOAM build artifacts. A pattern containing '/' is anchored to THIS
# directory, so bare `Make/linux*` only ever matched the root unit — hence the
# '**/' form, which covers every wmake unit (chorin_app, tests/*_unit, …)
# without needing a new line each time one is added.
**/Make/linux*
**/Make/darwin*
**/Make/win*

# Generated headers — the coupling cases' run.py emit these fresh into the
# solver tree via FOAM_ROOT. The cases themselves now live in
# thesis/notebooks/coupling/cases (this solver core holds no cases).
Model.H
NumericsKernels.H
UpdateAuxVariables.H
# Emitted march constants (mandate 6a) — zoomy_foam/_constants.py writes this
# from zoomy_core.solver.constants on every codegen, so it is a build product
# exactly like Model.H: never hand-edited, never committed.
MarchConstants.H

# Python cache (test scripts under tests/)
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# wmake artifacts of the function object
swePreciceCoupling/lnInclude/
Pressure.H
Corrector.H
ChorinState.H
.bincache/
*.egg-info/
zoomy_foam.egg-info/
/tests/chorin_bump/figures
